1
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:23,500
♫ As dusk starts, I look at the setting sun in the horizon ♫

2
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,660
♫  I faintly remember the outline of your face ♫

3
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:37,400
♫  After all, it can't be helped to feel more sentimental
when one reminisces  ♫

4
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:44,460
♫  I sigh softly at our happy times ♫

5
00:00:45,340 --> 00:00:51,900
♫  The night hasn't ended, so many stars fall into the
rim of my eyes  ♫

6
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:57,530
♫  Collecting a soft and gentle light  ♫

7
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:01,000
♫ The sky is clear, the scenery are good ♫

8
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,220
♫ If you're not by my side♫

9
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:11,200
♫ So what if I can go up the Firmament ♫

10
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:17,940
♫ The boat passes an empty harbor and feeds the loneliness ♫

11
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:24,710
♫ Frost falls over the wilderness, drooping the tears ♫

12
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:28,800
♫ Who caused my sun to fall from the sky ♫

13
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:39,090
♫ It’s your face that took away my entire light ♫

14
00:01:39,090 --> 00:01:45,000
♫ For only you are my heaven ♫

15
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:51,480
[Goodbye My Princess]

16
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:56,700
[Episode 43]

17
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,960
Here.

18
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:15,950
A'Du, you are not allowed to leave me again. You are not allowed to make me worry.

19
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:22,400
You must recover soon. When you feel better, we can go to Mi Luo Drinking House to drink.

20
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:35,800
Head of Court of Judicial Review Wang Shu greets Crown Princess Consort.

21
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:38,160
I am here by the emperor's request to

22
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:41,600
investigate the attempted assassination of the crown prince.

23
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:44,290
Miss A'Du fought with the assassin.

24
00:02:44,290 --> 00:02:47,420
I want to ask her a few questions.

25
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:51,000
A'Du, will you be able to?

26
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,590
Go ahead, Official Wang.

27
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:54,950
Yes.

28
00:02:55,700 --> 00:03:00,460
Did you clearly see the assassin's face the night of the assassination?

29
00:03:04,670 --> 00:03:08,430
Your Imperial Majesty, Miss A'Du said the assassin

30
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:11,240
was the empress' lady-in-waiting...

31
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,100
Rongshuang.

32
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:18,220
[Rongshuang]

33
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,650
- Search!
- Yes!

34
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:43,260
What are you doing?!

35
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:50,420
Empress, I came under the order of the emperor to arrest the assassin. Sorry, if I will be offending you greatly. Arrest her!

36
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:53,800
No! Preposterous! Who dares to touch her!

37
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:57,220
What proof do you have that Rongshuang is the assassin?

38
00:03:57,220 --> 00:04:01,400
- The witness A'Du woke up and identified Rongshuang as the assassin. Take her away!
- Go! Go! Hurry!

39
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,500
- No, you can't! Let go of Rongshuang!
- Empress! Empress!

40
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:05,500
- Let Rongshuang go!

41
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:09,080
Empress, you need to take care of yourself! Empress!

42
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:13,900
- Let Rongshuang go!
- Empress!

43
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:17,570
Empress, take care of yourself!

44
00:04:17,570 --> 00:04:21,620
- Let her go! Let go of Rongshuang! Let her go!
- Empress!

45
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:30,820
Imperial Doctor Wang, why hasn't the crown prince woken up yet?

46
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:33,160
Was the medication I gave you not effective?

47
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:40,820
Please forgive me Crown Princess Consort. I studied the medication.

48
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:45,500
This medication can help the wound heal quickly, but it is too strong.

49
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:48,160
The crown prince is a person of eminence.

50
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:51,780
We don't dare to use the medication on the crown prince.

51
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:56,800
You don't dare to use it? What time is it already? Are you all just going to watch him lay right there?

52
00:04:56,800 --> 00:05:00,290
My life is also at risk if I'm unable to cure the crown prince.

53
00:05:00,290 --> 00:05:03,090
Give me the medicine. If there are any consequences, I'll bear them!

54
00:05:03,090 --> 00:05:04,100
This...

55
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,300
Crown Princess Consort! This...

56
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,720
Give it to me!

57
00:05:21,210 --> 00:05:22,230
[Rongshuang]

58
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:29,920
Are you still not confessing?

59
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:37,470
I don't know when I offended the crown princess consort's lady-in-waiting.

60
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:39,600
Why would she frame me?

61
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:44,670
Your Imperial Majesty! That female servant from Xi State has only been in the palace for a year!

62
00:05:44,670 --> 00:05:50,300
How can we believe her words? Rongshuang has been by my side all these years. She would never do such a thing!

63
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:55,190
I saw the crown prince grow up. Why would I want to assassinate him?

64
00:05:55,190 --> 00:06:00,870
Do you think the crown prince and Miss A'Du would use their lives to frame you?

65
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:06,210
If it wasn't you, then you were ordered by someone.

66
00:06:06,210 --> 00:06:09,900
Tell me! Who ordered you to assassinate the crown prince?

67
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:13,090
If you still don't confess, I will be using torturous means.

68
00:06:13,090 --> 00:06:16,760
Chengyin is my son! Why would I kill him?

69
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:22,400
When Chengyin wakes up, we'll know why you wanted to kill him then.

70
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:26,790
Until we figure out the situation, you stay in Clean and Peaceful Palace!

71
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,330
Your Imperial Majesty!

72
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:44,500
The empress wants to assassinate the crown prince? Why?

73
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:48,900
All the information in the palace has been sealed off. Even I have no way of knowing things.

74
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:50,750
Does Ruyi not know either?

75
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:53,710
Sister is focusing on her pregnancy right now.

76
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:57,750
We shouldn't let her be bothered by these things for it might affect her pregnancy.

77
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:01,360
Father,

78
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:05,900
should we intervene in this matter and protect the empress?

79
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:11,330
Protect the empress? The empress is no longer of one mind with us.

80
00:07:11,330 --> 00:07:14,470
Assassinating the crown prince is a crime punishable by death.

81
00:07:14,470 --> 00:07:18,600
It's wiser to preserve ourselves. Let's not meddle in this trouble.

82
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:22,460
Moreover, my Ruyi is pregnant.

83
00:07:22,460 --> 00:07:26,310
Why would we still keep that worthless chess piece?

84
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:30,730
Send some gifts to the palace for Ruyi.

85
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:32,110
Yes.

86
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:39,500
Imperial Physician Wang, the crown prince's fever won't break and he keeps throwing up the medication.

87
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:53,760
Crown Princess Consort, the medication is too strong.

88
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:57,990
His Imperial Highness the Crown Prince is asthenic and cold. I fear that...

89
00:07:57,990 --> 00:08:03,000
he can't bear it. We all are at our wit's end.

90
00:08:09,150 --> 00:08:13,030
I understand. You are all dismissed.

91
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:14,400
Yes.

92
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,750
Li Chengyin, rest assured.

93
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:39,490
If you die, I will die alongside you.

94
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:45,330
The person you wish to see the most...

95
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:49,410
should be her, right?

96
00:08:53,180 --> 00:08:58,310
Just hold on for a little longer. I will get her for you.

97
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:03,350
I beg you to let me out!

98
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:05,450
Let me see His Imperial Highness the Crown Prince!

99
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:07,450
My Lady!

100
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,410
I will kneel to you all!

101
00:09:11,410 --> 00:09:14,540
I just beg you to tell His Imperial Majesty and the empress

102
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:17,180
to let me see the crown prince!

103
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:20,320
After I come back, I will accept any punishment.

104
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,610
Even if you lock me up for one year,

105
00:09:22,610 --> 00:09:26,610
three, five, ten years are all okay with me!

106
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:29,980
I just beg you to let me see His Imperial Highness just once!

107
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:32,210
- Crown Princess Consort.
- Just one glance!

108
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:34,910
I beg you all!

109
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:41,890
Jin'er, what should I do?

110
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:44,800
If His Imperial Highness suddenly dies,

111
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:47,570
I would not be able to live on.

112
00:09:47,570 --> 00:09:49,390
My Lady...

113
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:55,290
If the empress should punish anyone for this, I will bear it all.

114
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:58,620
Let her out.

115
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:00,190
Yes.

116
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:22,620
My Lady.

117
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:31,200
Go see His Imperial Highness.

118
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:35,150
How is he?

119
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,470
Tell me!

120
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:41,340
What happened to him?!

121
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:46,180
He only wishes to see you right now.

122
00:10:49,230 --> 00:10:52,130
My Lady! My Lady!

123
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,850
Crown Princess Consort.

124
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:07,430
You go inside.

125
00:11:08,970 --> 00:11:11,210
But do not cry anymore.

126
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,300
Thank you, Crown Princess Consort.

127
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:25,290
Hurry and go in.

128
00:11:54,010 --> 00:11:57,870
Crown Princess Consort, it is windy now. You should go back first.

129
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:04,090
Let Related Lady of Excellence Zhao stay here a bit longer.

130
00:12:04,090 --> 00:12:08,920
With Lady Zhao here, he will definitely recover.

131
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:42,030
Your Imperial Highness...

132
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:50,950
Hurry and wake up. Hurry and wake up.

133
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:55,660
I beg you.

134
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:58,200
Hurry and wake up.

135
00:13:00,690 --> 00:13:05,690
If you do not wake up, what will happen to me?

136
00:13:07,290 --> 00:13:09,000
Your Imperial Highness...

137
00:13:42,010 --> 00:13:45,750
Crown Princess Consort, it is not very good to let commoner Zhao stay here for too long.

138
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:48,120
Have her return to her palace earlier.

139
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:51,280
I will go in now.

140
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:01,480
Then, I will leave now.

141
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:17,180
The wind is actually this big...

142
00:15:10,830 --> 00:15:16,450
Li Chengyin, people are really very strange sometimes.

143
00:15:16,450 --> 00:15:20,520
Before, whenever we saw each other, we would argue.

144
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:23,550
The only thing I would think about was how much you angered me.

145
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:26,900
But now that you are lying here in front of me,

146
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:30,000
my eyes are only filled with all the good deeds you did to me.

147
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:41,550
Actually, I did not hate you from the moment I saw you.

148
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:44,620
I still remember that day

149
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:48,570
when Yongniang told me that you would soon become the crown prince.

150
00:15:48,570 --> 00:15:51,370
I was actually quite happy,

151
00:15:51,370 --> 00:15:57,360
even though I knew back then that the person you liked was Lady Zhao.

152
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:01,880
And then not long after that,

153
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:08,720
I heard about how you attacked Danchi.

154
00:16:09,590 --> 00:16:12,490
I really wanted to kill you with a slash of a sword.

155
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:25,080
Do you still remember the night we married?

156
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:27,260
You were in front of me.

157
00:16:27,260 --> 00:16:29,060
I looked at you.

158
00:16:29,060 --> 00:16:31,330
And in my heart I thought,

159
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:36,050
"Should I just stab and kill you now?"

160
00:16:37,490 --> 00:16:42,680
I hated you, but I hated myself even more.

161
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:45,650
I hated that I could not do it.

162
00:16:47,170 --> 00:16:51,160
I hated myself for I seemed to have liked you a bit.

163
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:57,870
Hurry and wake up, okay?

164
00:16:58,780 --> 00:17:00,750
What you said is right.

165
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:03,730
I am quite afraid of being a young widow.

166
00:17:03,730 --> 00:17:08,680
In Xi State, the women whose husbands that had died,

167
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:11,990
had to marry their husband's younger brother.

168
00:17:11,990 --> 00:17:15,080
But if you really die like this,

169
00:17:18,120 --> 00:17:20,890
who else would I be able to marry?

170
00:17:23,330 --> 00:17:26,160
How can I marry someone else?

171
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:31,270
Won't I really become a young widow for the rest of my life?

172
00:17:33,050 --> 00:17:36,460
I also have a secret I have not told you yet.

173
00:17:38,690 --> 00:17:43,790
When I was young, Lady Mingyuan taught me words from the Central Plains, but no matter what, I just could not learn them.

174
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:46,580
After I came here, it was still the same.

175
00:17:46,580 --> 00:17:52,130
All I did was mechanically copy each and every stroke.

176
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:56,380
For example, your name.

177
00:17:56,380 --> 00:18:00,020
The "yin" from Li Chengyin.

178
00:18:01,990 --> 00:18:06,510
At first, I thought it was read as "qin."

179
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:11,820
I heard that the people of the Central Plains are very particular about naming their children.

180
00:18:11,820 --> 00:18:16,540
What does your character, "yin," mean?

181
00:18:18,580 --> 00:18:22,910
- Yin State.
- Yin State.

182
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:29,790
The founder of the dynasty

183
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:33,540
was originally from Yin State.

184
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:40,140
It is east of Central State and south of Liang State.

185
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:44,220
It is the place from where the dragon (symbol of the emperor) prevailed,

186
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,050
so...

187
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:51,520
that is why I am called "Chengyin."

188
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:58,000
I am not dreaming! I am not dreaming!

189
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,870
You are awake?

190
00:18:59,870 --> 00:19:05,180
Li Chengyin, you are awake. Li Chengyin, you are awake.

191
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:10,450
You are awake. You are awake.

192
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:22,120
Hurry and summon the imperial physician! Shi'en, hurry and summon the imperial physician!

193
00:19:23,090 --> 00:19:24,480
- What happened, Crown Princess Consort?
- What's wrong?

194
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:26,550
The crown prince is awake!

195
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:29,510
Your Imperial Highness the Crown Prince! Your Highness!

196
00:19:30,730 --> 00:19:31,890
Your Highness!

197
00:19:31,890 --> 00:19:33,770
Do not cry.

198
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:44,370
Crown Princess Consort, do not cry.

199
00:19:44,370 --> 00:19:46,730
Everything is fine now.

200
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:59,480
Your Imperial Highness, you are awake?

201
00:20:00,310 --> 00:20:02,080
Your Highness.

202
00:20:05,220 --> 00:20:07,120
Sese,

203
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:11,650
why did you come here?

204
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:14,850
It was Crown Princess Consort who let me come.

205
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:17,900
She wanted me to stay and be by your side.

206
00:20:25,210 --> 00:20:26,990
I am fine now.

207
00:20:26,990 --> 00:20:30,050
His Imperial Majesty has arrived!

208
00:20:37,490 --> 00:20:38,820
You are all dismissed.

209
00:20:38,820 --> 00:20:40,550
Yes.

210
00:20:42,230 --> 00:20:44,080
Imperial Father.

211
00:20:52,750 --> 00:20:54,610
How are you?

212
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:58,660
I am a lot better now.

213
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:06,760
A'Du has already identified who tried to assassinate you.

214
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:12,120
It was the empress' servant, Rongshuang.

215
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:43,190
What do you mean?

216
00:21:43,190 --> 00:21:47,860
You still remember this jade pendant, right?

217
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:50,910
This was left by my biological mother.

218
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:57,110
Originally, this jade pendant only had one half.

219
00:21:57,110 --> 00:22:03,920
The other half was given to me by Aunt Mingyuan when I went to Xi State.

220
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:10,270
At her deathbed, Aunt Mingyuan told me

221
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:14,820
that the person who caused my mother to die

222
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:19,270
was the empress.

223
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:32,250
Rongshuang, how dare you be so extremely bold as to assassinate the crown prince?!

224
00:22:32,250 --> 00:22:35,660
His Imperial Majesty is here now. What more have you got to say?

225
00:22:36,150 --> 00:22:38,330
Your Imperial Majesty, Rongshuang has been framed.

226
00:22:38,330 --> 00:22:39,950
It was not me. It really was not me.

227
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:43,550
I really did not try to assassinate the crown prince! I plead for Your Imperial Majesty to give me justice!

228
00:22:43,550 --> 00:22:46,720
The evidence is here. It is irrefutable.

229
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:51,390
Tell me! Who was it who ordered you to assassinate the crown prince?

230
00:22:51,390 --> 00:22:53,010
No one ordered me.

231
00:22:53,010 --> 00:22:55,560
The person I wanted to murder was not the crown prince,

232
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:59,360
but... but the crown princess consort.

233
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:02,510
The crown princess consort is barbaric and unreasonable. She treated me disrespectfully on many occasions.

234
00:23:02,510 --> 00:23:04,810
That is why I wanted to kill her.

235
00:23:06,140 --> 00:23:09,400
You went to the crown prince's palace to assassinate the crown princess consort?

236
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:13,580
How did you know that the crown princess consort would be there?

237
00:23:13,580 --> 00:23:15,060
I followed her there.

238
00:23:15,060 --> 00:23:16,740
That is a bunch of nonsense!

239
00:23:16,740 --> 00:23:20,510
I am really telling the truth! I would not dare to deceive His Imperial Majesty!

240
00:23:22,410 --> 00:23:25,140
You do not dare betray your emperor?

241
00:23:25,140 --> 00:23:28,650
Let me ask you one question.

242
00:23:28,650 --> 00:23:32,320
Was it or was it not the empress who instigated you?

243
00:23:33,390 --> 00:23:35,830
This affair has nothing to do with the empress!

244
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:38,260
Your Imperial Majesty, please do not listen to the slanders of villains!

245
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:40,670
The empress and you have had deep spousal relations for so many years.

246
00:23:40,670 --> 00:23:44,470
Your Imperial Majesty, you must believe the empress!

247
00:23:45,380 --> 00:23:49,790
The crown prince has already woken.

248
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:30,730
Your Imperial Majesty, has this case been thoroughly investigated?

249
00:24:30,730 --> 00:24:33,690
It has nothing to do with Rongshuang, correct?

250
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:36,100
I'm asking you...

251
00:24:36,100 --> 00:24:40,400
That year, when Pure Consort was being plotted against,

252
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:43,420
which we found out later that she had consumed lethal poison,

253
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:48,280
this poison... was it given by you?

254
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:53,030
It wasn't me. Your Imperial Majesty, please do not listen to the nonsense of those people around you.

255
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:58,680
Yuyao and you were close as sisters.

256
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:01,860
You even raised Chengyin to adulthood.

257
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:07,570
I have always thought that you were a magnanimous empress,

258
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,230
until...

259
00:25:11,320 --> 00:25:15,470
Mingyuan told Chengyin the truth.

260
00:25:15,470 --> 00:25:19,530
Only then did I know that.

261
00:25:20,730 --> 00:25:26,060
I had kept a poisonous snake by my side.

262
00:25:27,970 --> 00:25:29,420
Your Imperial Majesty...

263
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:31,540
Isn't it enough that you caused the death of Yuyao?

264
00:25:31,540 --> 00:25:36,110
Today, you still try to kill Chengyin? You are really ruthless!

265
00:25:39,030 --> 00:25:43,400
Your Imperial Majesty, we have been married for more than thirty years.

266
00:25:44,450 --> 00:25:47,670
I never expected that in your heart,

267
00:25:48,810 --> 00:25:51,440
I am held in such a deplorable opinion.

268
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:53,970
You have always been so deplorable!

269
00:25:53,970 --> 00:25:58,700
I have never questioned you about anything in the inner palace, but it doesn't mean that I didn't know anything!

270
00:25:59,940 --> 00:26:04,700
All this while, I thought that because you wanted to defend yourself,

271
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:09,070
that is why you came up with so many ploys.

272
00:26:09,070 --> 00:26:16,090
If Chengyin can't even deal with all these, how is he worthy to assume the position of the emperor?

273
00:26:16,090 --> 00:26:21,360
But I... never imagined that

274
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:26,780
you were actually someone who was insane and ridiculous!

275
00:26:26,780 --> 00:26:32,570
You could even bear to kill your own son!

276
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:37,980
Your Imperial Majesty, I didn't do it!

277
00:26:37,980 --> 00:26:43,240
How could I bear to kill Chengyin?

278
00:26:43,240 --> 00:26:46,040
I love him more than anyone else!

279
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:48,200
If you do not believe me,

280
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:51,640
please have this case investigated thoroughly and return justice to me!

281
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:53,550
Stop acting!

282
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:58,250
Do you really want me to have you brought to the Court of Judicial Review and be interrogated before you'll confess?

283
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:09,670
For the sake of our married relationship of more than thirty years, I will not take your life!

284
00:27:11,570 --> 00:27:16,840
Your Imperial Majesty, I have been falsely accused!

285
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:18,960
I am really being falsely accused!

286
00:27:18,960 --> 00:27:23,570
I have already written the edict to abolish your empress status.

287
00:27:23,570 --> 00:27:27,660
I will announce it at the imperial court tomorrow.

288
00:27:27,660 --> 00:27:30,950
No, Your Imperial Majesty!

289
00:27:32,020 --> 00:27:37,530
Even if you've written an edict, the chancellery won't promulgate it that soon.

290
00:27:37,530 --> 00:27:39,380
And my uncle...

291
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:41,690
He would not just sit idly and be indifferent.

292
00:27:41,690 --> 00:27:44,160
You still are putting your hope on that uncle of yours?

293
00:27:45,870 --> 00:27:48,500
Lady of Brevy Gao is already pregnant.

294
00:27:48,500 --> 00:27:52,750
She will be bestowed with the title of Noble Consort very soon.

295
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:56,720
One of you is a niece who has not given birth to a prince before,

296
00:27:56,720 --> 00:28:00,900
the other is a daughter who is pregnant with the emperor's son.

297
00:28:00,900 --> 00:28:04,600
Who do you think Prime Minister Gao will choose?

298
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:21,180
Your Imperial Majesty! Your Imperial Majesty!

299
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:23,420
I have always treated you wholeheartedly!

300
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:26,660
Go away! Get lost! What wholeheartedly?

301
00:28:26,660 --> 00:28:29,680
If you treated me wholeheartedly, would you murder my most beloved woman

302
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:32,050
and kill your son?!

303
00:28:33,230 --> 00:28:39,010
Up until now, everything was caused by yourself! You harmed yourself!

304
00:28:39,010 --> 00:28:41,740
Now your uncle, your relatives, are all distancing themselves from you.

305
00:28:41,740 --> 00:28:45,210
In the harem, there is no one left who will speak for you.

306
00:28:45,210 --> 00:28:49,910
Even more so, no one will want to get close to you now because your palace maid has been caned to death!

307
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:56,090
However, you are still my wife. I will now give you two choices.

308
00:28:56,090 --> 00:29:01,250
Either, starting today, we will completely seal your palace and imprison you inside.

309
00:29:01,250 --> 00:29:05,130
We'll get someone who's deaf and mute to bring your meals to you!

310
00:29:05,130 --> 00:29:09,890
You will then spend the rest of your life in this manner!

311
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:12,300
Or...

312
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:46,490
I, Meiniang, have been betrothed to His Majesty since childhood.

313
00:29:46,490 --> 00:29:50,380
Ever since I first laid eyes on you,

314
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:56,380
I have never had anyone else in my heart.

315
00:29:56,380 --> 00:30:02,400
I know Your Imperial Majesty has always loved Pure Consort Gu.

316
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:05,460
But these many years,

317
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:12,460
you have always taken care of me with affection.

318
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:21,620
I only want to know,

319
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:32,550
if I was ever in your heart.

320
00:30:35,970 --> 00:30:40,290
You know the answer in your heart.

321
00:30:40,290 --> 00:30:42,590
No need to ask me.

322
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:03,410
Your Imperial Majesty!!

323
00:31:27,460 --> 00:31:32,270
Empress of the Zhang clan is filled with resentment and brought disaster to the imperial harem.

324
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:35,800
She disobeyed the decree on numerous occasions, unable to appease and cherish the children of others.

325
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:38,310
If there's a sparrow hawk (ruthless and evil) in the inner palace,

326
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:40,210
there isn't any virtue of the ospreys (fair and moral),

327
00:31:40,210 --> 00:31:41,950
but murderous actions like that of Empresses Lv and Huo (both are Han dynasty empresses).

328
00:31:41,950 --> 00:31:45,210
She's not suitable to respectfully bear such grand worship.

329
00:32:06,890 --> 00:32:10,330
Today, I'm ordering the Court of the Imperial Family to clean up the filth and fulfill their duty.

330
00:32:10,330 --> 00:32:13,580
Today, the official seal of empress is being taken back from her.

331
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:16,640
For the sake that she has come into the palace and served for a long time,

332
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:20,290
she is spared the death sentence and will live in the side palace.

333
00:32:20,290 --> 00:32:25,630
Until she dies, she will not be allowed out of it. End of decree!

334
00:33:00,050 --> 00:33:06,240
[Clean and Peaceful Palace]

335
00:33:29,030 --> 00:33:30,920
Who is it?

336
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:36,090
Chengyin? Is that you?

337
00:33:44,130 --> 00:33:45,820
Who is it!

338
00:33:45,820 --> 00:33:47,990
Is it Chengyin?

339
00:33:47,990 --> 00:33:52,390
Chengyin? Is that you?

340
00:33:52,390 --> 00:33:54,480
It's me.

341
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:01,680
Chengyin...

342
00:34:03,420 --> 00:34:04,970
Back then,

343
00:34:04,970 --> 00:34:08,700
it was indeed because of my selfish reasons

344
00:34:08,700 --> 00:34:11,630
that I caused the death of your mother.

345
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:17,940
But these years, I treated you as my own and raised you with great care.

346
00:34:17,940 --> 00:34:22,520
I placed all my heart and expectations on you.

347
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:28,180
I really wanted you to become the wise ruler of the future.

348
00:34:28,180 --> 00:34:30,010
You're right.

349
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:35,920
These years, you did raise me with great care.

350
00:34:37,550 --> 00:34:42,880
But all those things should have been given to me by my own mother!

351
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:45,600
You took my mother's life

352
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:49,270
and took away the happiness that should have belonged to me.

353
00:34:52,790 --> 00:34:55,210
Do you know...

354
00:34:55,210 --> 00:34:59,750
how much I hoped you wouldn't hire someone to assassinate me,

355
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:04,900
how much I hoped that you truly treated me as your son?

356
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:08,830
But I was wrong.

357
00:35:10,810 --> 00:35:13,650
I was completely wrong.

358
00:35:17,300 --> 00:35:18,950
This stab...

359
00:35:18,950 --> 00:35:21,630
has woken me up.

360
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:23,550
Chengyin! Chengyin!

361
00:35:23,550 --> 00:35:29,040
I was only a pawn to help protect your own position.

362
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:35,550
I was only a chip you used to retain Imperial Father's affections!

363
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:39,810
To you, my life meant nothing!

364
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:46,840
You never thought of me as your own son.

365
00:35:56,880 --> 00:36:00,960
[Clean and Peaceful Palace]

366
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:09,950
I thank you for all the years that you've raised and cared for me.

367
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:13,860
Chengyin!

368
00:36:15,020 --> 00:36:16,650
Chengyin!

369
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:25,030
With that stab, I've returned half a life to you.

370
00:36:28,330 --> 00:36:30,800
We are cleared from any debts to each other now.

371
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,200
Chengyin!

372
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:47,130
From now onward, the fate we share as mother and son has come to an end.

373
00:36:52,810 --> 00:36:58,690
Chengyin! Chengyin! Chengyin!

374
00:36:58,690 --> 00:37:01,880
Chengyin! Chengyin, come back!

375
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:04,520
Come back, my son!

376
00:37:04,520 --> 00:37:09,240
Chengyin! My son!

377
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:11,570
Come back!!

378
00:37:13,820 --> 00:37:16,940
Please come back!

379
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:21,330
My son...

380
00:37:49,300 --> 00:37:52,520
Reporting to Your Imperial Majesty, the empress...

381
00:37:55,110 --> 00:37:58,590
Wrong... Commoner Zhang passed away just now.

382
00:38:02,930 --> 00:38:04,990
Did she leave any last words?

383
00:38:06,370 --> 00:38:08,440
None at all.

384
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:15,930
[Jade Collecting Palace Hall]

385
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:00,650
Shi‘en, please get up first.

386
00:40:00,650 --> 00:40:02,210
Yes.

387
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:06,420
It's not that I do not want to go with you and visit him.

388
00:40:06,420 --> 00:40:11,260
It's just that... in a time like this, it's useless no matter who visits him.

389
00:40:11,260 --> 00:40:13,230
It's good for him to be quiet by himself.

390
00:40:13,230 --> 00:40:14,700
But...

391
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:18,170
Don't worry. Nothing will happen to him.

392
00:40:18,170 --> 00:40:23,410
He needs to be able to cry freely before this matter will pass.

393
00:40:23,410 --> 00:40:28,780
Yes. You are the one who understands His Imperial Highness best. I'll believe in whatever you say.

394
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:54,070
Related Lady of Excellence.

395
00:40:54,070 --> 00:40:57,620
Congratulations to My Lady for resuming the position of Related Lady of Excellence.

396
00:40:57,620 --> 00:41:01,150
Jin'er, I am going to visit His Imperial Highness the Crown Prince.

397
00:41:06,330 --> 00:41:10,020
