398
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:40,830
Your Imperial Highness, I can finally see you.

399
00:41:40,830 --> 00:41:44,240
The hard times are finally over, and the good times are just beginning.

400
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:47,430
No one will separate us again.

401
00:42:06,700 --> 00:42:10,400
You really suffered much during this period.

402
00:42:11,950 --> 00:42:16,670
Your Imperial Highness, when you went through such life-threatening danger, I couldn't eat or sleep each day.

403
00:42:16,670 --> 00:42:21,840
From now onward, I want to be with Your Imperial Highness in both life and death.

404
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:24,480
I will never leave Your Highness even for a step.

